sshfu: ssh config manager

This is an early early POC, both as in proof of concept, and
as in piece of crap. Be foolish at you own peril.

Example syntax:
host server address server.test user root
host grimalkin address 192.168.1.1 gw server user cma
host vm1 address 10.10.1.1 gw grimalkin

